<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT-ACX Tech cut to market outperform.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT-ACX Tech cut to market outperform.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Goldman Sachs said it cut ACX Technologies Inc to market outperform from its recommended list.</p>
<p>-- Earlier on Friday ACX said it would take a $15-$25 million fourth quarter charge to restructure its Golden Technologies Co Inc subsidiary.</p>
<p>-- ACX dropped 2-1/4 to 17-5/8 in early trading.</p>
<p>((-- Wall Street Desk 212-859-1730))</p>
